creator: Energy Schweiz
descriptionHtml:
Vintage Radio brings you iconic hits and classics with the best from the 60ies, the 70ies, the 80ies until the 90ies. You hear nonstop music with all the great songs from Abba, Rolling Stones, Madonna, Tina Turner, Queen and Phil Collins, all the way to Elton John or Roxette on your smartphone or tablet computer at no costs.

In the app you get additional information about the artists, you can share your favorite tracks and mark them to display them conveniently in your collection.

Save data volume by activating "data saver" in the settings.

And as an extra, you can listen to more of Switzerland’s most popular DAB+ programs and discover more great music with Luna, Radio Del Mar, Schlager Radio, Classix Radio and Rockit Radio.
descriptionShort: The best songs of all times 24/7 oldies

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We love beautiful designs! That's why we improve Vintage Radio all the time and make it even prettier.
This time though, we have improved the performance and fixed some bugs.
Good ideas are always welcome! Tell us what you think and write a review on the App Store. Or use the contact form directly in the App to let us know if something doesn't work.

Thank you for listening to Vintage Radio. Upgrade to the latest version and enjoy these new features and improvements:

• Introduction of CMP/OneTrust for better data protection
• Bugfixes and updates of services

Good ideas are always welcome! Tell us what you think and write a review in the App Store. Or use the contact form directly in the App to let us know if something doesn't work.

title: Vintage Radio Oldies 80s Hits

creator: Energy Schweiz
descriptionHtml:
Vintage Radio brings you iconic hits and classics with the best from the 60ies, the 70ies, the 80ies until the 90ies. You hear nonstop music with all the great songs from Abba, Rolling Stones, Madonna, Tina Turner, Queen and Phil Collins, all the way to Elton John or Roxette on your smartphone or tablet computer at no costs.

In the app you get additional information about the artists, you can share your favorite tracks and see what songs have been — or are about to be played.

Save data volume by activating "data saver" in the settings.

Use the sleeptimer to listen to Vintage Radio while falling asleep — the app automatically turns off the music after a certain time, set by you.

And as an extra, you can listen to more of Switzerland’s most popular DAB+ programs and discover more great music with Schlager Radio and Rockit Radio.
